@startuml
class ImageProcessor {
    -original_image: Image
    -current_image: Image
    -history: list
    +load_image(path)
    +adjust_brightness(factor)
    +adjust_contrast(factor)
    +resize(w, h)
    +reset()
    +save(path)
    +get_info()
}

class ImageEditor {
    -processor: ImageProcessor
    -brightness: QSlider
    -contrast: QSlider
    -w_spin, h_spin: QSpinBox
    +load_image()
    +apply_all_changes()
    +display_current_image()
    +schedule_update()
}

ImageEditor --> ImageProcessor : использует
ImageProcessor --> PIL.Image
ImageEditor --> QLabel
@enduml